{
  "stem": "11722.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "When we left the place of work, they counted us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "As we entered the camp again, they counted us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We had to line up in front of every barrack.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They counted us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And after that, they gave us our bread, which was a piece of black bread.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Sometimes it had a slice of margarine with it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Sometimes a slice of liverwurst.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And that was our meager rations.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It was a starving rations.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I don't know how many calories, but it just wasn't enough to-- to survive on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I was one of the youngest ones in the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Eventually, I moved from this power plant.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I worked in a coal mine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I was switching tracks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I was a kid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "There was a civil Polish engineer who would give me a piece of bread once in awhile.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I would help out in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Now that I look back, maybe fellow inmates saw to it that I'd get a job, that I [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] survive.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "We didn't think that we could-- anybody would ever survive these unsurvivable conditions.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "But I was given a chance.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And I was a little bit better off than most.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And they wanted me, perhaps, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] to be a eyewitness to what took place.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I was-- I-- I witnessed father and son fighting over a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Son stealing from the father.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I witnessed what went on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "I was sort of glad that I wasn't with my father and my brother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "It reminds me of a drowning man-- somebody trying to save him, and they both drown.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I was-- I had a bad tooth.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I remember I went to the Krankenbau.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Two guys held me down, and somebody yanked out, without any Novocaine.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
